    {"content_type": "Decision", "content": "决定将后端从 Node.js 迁移到 Rust，因为性能瓶颈明显。", "importance": 0.85, "category": "tech_decisions"},
    {"content_type": "Decision", "content": "存储层从 RocksDB 迁移到 redb，编译更简单且纯 Rust。", "importance": 0.80, "category": "tech_decisions"},
    {"content_type": "Decision", "content": "全文检索选用 Tantivy，BM25 算法比简单关键词匹配强。", "importance": 0.75, "category": "tech_decisions"},
    {"content_type": "Decision", "content": "API 层用 gRPC 而非 REST，需要强类型契约和流式传输。", "importance": 0.70, "category": "tech_decisions"},
    {"content_type": "Decision", "content": "索引加载改为 mmap + lazy page fault，预计内存降到 200MB。", "importance": 0.90, "category": "tech_decisions"},
    {"content_type": "Decision", "content": "选择 DashScope text-embedding-v4 作为语义后端，1024 维向量质量好。", "importance": 0.78, "category": "tech_decisions"},
    {"content_type": "Decision", "content": "用 jieba 分词支持中文，放弃纯空格分词方案。", "importance": 0.72, "category": "tech_decisions"},
