    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "HIPPMEM 是一个 Rust 原生关联记忆引擎，给 AI Agent 长期记忆。", "importance": 0.90, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "项目启动于 2025 年，核心思路是写入时发现关联而非检索时拼凑。", "importance": 0.85, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "hippmem 使用 redb 做嵌入式存储，避免外部数据库依赖。", "importance": 0.78, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "引擎支持 14 种关联边类型，包括实体重叠、主题重叠、因果等。", "importance": 0.75, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "扩散激活算法基于 Collins & Loftus 的语义网络模型。", "importance": 0.72, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "支持三种检索模式：Fast（单跳）、Balanced、Deep（多跳扩散）。", "importance": 0.70, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "记忆演化采用 Hebbian 学习 + 时间衰减 + 摘要压缩。", "importance": 0.68, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "可解释性通过 matched_dimensions + activation_trace 实现五问诊断。", "importance": 0.65, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "全文索引基于 Tantivy，中文分词用 jieba-rs。", "importance": 0.62, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "Embedding 后端支持 DashScope、OpenAI 兼容和确定性降级。", "importance": 0.60, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "评测框架支持 10 类任务：事实回忆、因果追溯、隐式联想等。", "importance": 0.58, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "引擎默认不依赖网络，可在完全离线环境运行。", "importance": 0.55, "category": "project_knowledge"},
    {"content_type": "ProjectKnowledge", "content": "所有配置通过 .env 文件或环境变量注入，无需硬编码。", "importance": 0.45, "category": "project_knowledge"},
